quran[10{c,v,t}:
7,58,jo zameen achi hoti hai woh apne rab ke hukum se khoob phal phool latayen hai aur jo zameen kharab hoti hai a seen se naaqis pedawar ke siwa kuch nahi nikalta is terhan hum nshanyon ko baar baar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo shukar guzaar honay walay hain
7,59,"hum ne Nooh ko uss ki qoum ki taraf bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai mein tumahray haq mein aik holnaak din ke azaab se darta hon """
7,60,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne jawab diya"" hum ko to yeh nazar aata hai ke tum Sarih gumraahi mein mubtala ho """
7,61,"Nooh ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, mein kisi gumraahi mein nahi para ho n balkay, mein rab alaalmin ka rasool hon"
7,62,"tumhe apne rab ke paighamaat pohanchata hon, tumhara kher khuwa hon aur mujhe Allah ki taraf se woh kuch maloom hai jo tumhen maloom nahi hai"
7,63,"kya tumhe is baat par taajjub howa ke tumahray paas khud tumhari apni qoum ke aik aadmi ke zareya se tumahray rab ki yaad dehani aayi taakay tumhe khabardaar kere aur tum ghalat rawi se bach jao aur tum par reham kya jaye? """
7,64,"magar unhon ne is ko jhutla diya aakhir-kaar hum ne usay aur is ke sathiyon ko aik kashti mein nijaat di aur unn logon ko duubo diya jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya tha, yaqeenan woh andhay log thay"
7,65,"aur Aad ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai hood ko bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran قو m, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai phir kya tum ghalat rawi se parhaiz nah karo ge? """
7,66,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar rahay thay, jawab mein kaha"" hum to tumhe be aqli mein mubtala samajte hain aur hamein gumaan hai ke tum jhutay ho """
7,67,"is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, mein be aqli mein mubtala nahi hon balkay mein rab alaalmin ka rasool hon"
